sources.title: Western Movie | The Spitfire (1960) | Michael Landon, Lorne Greene, Pernell Roberts | Bonanza
sources.description:
A family seeks revenge against Joe for shooting the treacherous patriarch in self-defense after the man tried to set fire to the Ponderosa. Jack Elam and Katherine Warren guest star..
 
Director: William D. Faralla 
Writer: Ward Hawkins
Stars: Michael Landon, Lorne Greene, Pernell Roberts 
Genres: Classics, Cult, TV, Western
